{
  "stem": "11964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nevertheless, we took a lot of things with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother said, you know, I have a cousin to the east of Radomsko in a town named Konskie.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we looked for anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some kind of a vehicle to take us east of Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sure enough, a neighbor of ours found a pickup truck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we shared the pickup truck with him, and we went to Konskie.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We arrived in Konskie Friday night, which was Shabbat, which was a no no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which was something that nobody would do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, when we arrived there, they just were overwhelmed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't understand how we would have dared to come to their home, into the Shabbat already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we explained to them that the Germans are really coming, and they were incredulous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They really didn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, we stayed through the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And sure enough, two days after we got there, the Germans got there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was one of the very first horrors that we experienced, because the Germans went to all the homes of the father-- most prominent Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They came to my mother's cousin's-- his name was Rafalowicz-- to his house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had four sons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took all the males out of the house, including my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took them to the outskirts of town, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was happening with all these people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were waiting for their return.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And sure enough, they came back at the end of the day, ashen gray.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My father was there, and the boys were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the boys and my father had to dig a trench after they had killed the father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, that was the shock of our lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
